Notice No. CMS-29

March 6, 2002


COMMODITY EXCHANGE, INC.


SWITCH OF GUARANTEE


Please be advised that effective immediately, March 6, 2002, William Bradt

(BIGE-982) will no longer be guaranteed by Man International, Inc.  However,

Mr. Bradt will remain a member guaranteed by FC Stone, LLC.


In connection therewith, notification of any claims against the

aforementioned individual arising out of transactions executed on the

Exchange up to the close of business on February 21, 2002, must be submitted

to the Corporate Secretary's Office within the (10) days.


Inquiries regarding the above should be directed to the Member Services

Department at 212-299-2370.
